   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Sarapammon, son of Horion, has brought one basket (sargane) of chaff for burning, equal 1. Year 13 and 1, Mesore 12. The same has brought to the bank of the river for the 13th and 1st year, for the village of Karanis, one sargane of chaff for burning. (2nd hand) I, Neilos, have signed. (3rd hand) I, Heron, have signed.</ab>
